title: Minnesota: Land of Trend Thousand Lakes 12/3: Ron DeSantis, Joel Osteen, Red Notice, Salt Bae, John Eastman, Ethan Crumbley
itunes:title: Minnesota: Land of Trend Thousand Lakes 12/3: Ron DeSantis, Joel Osteen, Red Notice, Salt Bae, John Eastman, Ethan Crumbley
description:
In this edition of Minnesota: Land of Trend Thousand Lakes, Jack and Miles discuss Ron DeSantis suggesting Florida get its own military, Joel Osteen's toilets overflowing with money, the complete lack of buzz around 'Red Notice', the 'Salt Bae' restaurant manager justifying their high prices, John Eastman pleading the 5th, and Ethan Crumbley's parents being charged with manslaughter
